#7945
gray glowing scars man~
Ardraum the Vengeful~
Ardraum stands here in a weathered gray cloak, various scars adorning his forarms and face glowing soflty with amber light.
~
   Ardraum stands before you loosely wrapped in a weathered gray cloak that
barely covers his broad shoulders.  Underneath the worn cloak, he is wearing a
dark shirt and a very dark, armored vest.  The material of the vest is hard to
pinpoint as its surface seems to absorb all light.  Brown leather pants cover
his legs, and the ornately worked hilt of a large knife in a scabbard hangs
from a heavy black leather belt.  A tight cropped beard of dark brown, wiry
hair adorns the hard expression on his face which contrasts his clean shaven
head.  Remarkably, his eyes seem to emit an amber glow and a circular scar on
his forehead is outlined in the same honeyed amber glow.  The sleeves of his
dark shirt are rolled up to expose his lean, muscular forearms that are
covered in terrible scars that seem to also emit the same honeyed-amber glow.

~
