#7982
nyarlathotep chaos man shadow~
Nyarlathotep~
A shadowy figure is floating here. The dark edges of his physical presence undulate ominously.
~
The crawling chaos.  The king of shadows.  Once known as Nyarlathotep, this
being is now a ghost of what he once was.  The horrors he brought upon the
world during his life could never be understated, and it is the echo of these
horrors that perpetuate his being now.  Partially shadow, partially material,
the edges of his vaguely man-shaped form are shifting and pulsating, making
him difficult to focus on.  Just when you think you know exactly what you're
looking at, his chaotic form becomes something slightly different.  
~
